= Mix_Playing =

Check the status of a specific channel.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int Mix_Playing(int channel);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''channel'''
|channel
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns number of channel playings

== Remarks ==

If the specified channel is -1, check all channels.

